HEADWORD: do-it-yourself
<hw>do-it-yourself</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>performed or made by an
end-user who is without professional training in the relevant
techniques; <as>as, their house was a <ex>do-it-yourself</ex>
project</as>. Contrasted with <contr>factory-made</contr> and
<contr>professional</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

